Our colors and themes are inspired by the painfully 90's color choices of the R
Foundation, particularly [its logo](https://www.r-project.org/logo/), and the 
Rust Foundation's official [brand guide](https://rustfoundation.org/brand-guide/). 

## Colors

We have defined several utility classes to make using consistent colors easier.
These can be used to define background and text colors. They are also used to
define semantic colors, which are applied automatically. 

